# Wisp

Single Rust binary (`wisp`) that turns PRDs into Pull Requests using AI coding agents (Claude Code or Gemini CLI), Ralph Loops, and Dev Containers.

## Structure

- `Cargo.toml` — Rust project manifest
- `src/main.rs` — Entry point, CLI dispatch, generator commands
- `src/cli.rs` — Clap derive structs for all subcommands
- `src/config.rs` — `.env` loading, env var resolution, defaults
- `src/pipeline/orchestrator.rs` — Manifest dispatch, order sequencing, parallel execution
- `src/pipeline/runner.rs` — Single PRD x repo pipeline (clone, branch, agents, PR)
- `src/pipeline/agent.rs` — Ralph Loop (prompt assembly, completion detection)
- `src/pipeline/devcontainer.rs` — Dev Container lifecycle (RAII cleanup)
- `src/pipeline/mod.rs` — Agent ordering, blocking/non-blocking classification
- `src/provider/` — AI provider abstraction (Provider trait, Claude, Gemini)
- `src/git/` — Clone, branch, rebase, PR creation, evidence comments
- `src/manifest/mod.rs` — Manifest JSON parsing (serde)
- `src/prd/mod.rs` — PRD metadata extraction
- `src/context/mod.rs` — Context skill assembly, frontmatter stripping
- `src/logging/` — JSONL formatting, log tailing, tracing setup
- `src/utils.rs` — Async exec helpers, repo name extraction
- `agents/` — Agent prompt markdown files (`_base-system.md` + per-agent `prompt.md`)
- `templates/` — PRD, manifest, and context templates
- `skills/` — Cursor-compatible agent skills (SKILL.md format)
- `.devcontainer/` — Dev Container config (firewall, setup hooks — only remaining shell)
- `scripts/install.sh` — Binary download installer
- `.github/workflows/` — CI (test/clippy/fmt) and release (cross-compile, GitHub Releases)
- `config/` — AI CLI settings templates
- `.mcp.json` — MCP server configuration (GitHub, Notion, Figma, Slack)

## Pipeline Flow

```
Description → wisp generate prd → PRDs + Manifest
Manifest → wisp orchestrate → [Architect → Designer → Migration → Developer → Accessibility → Tester → Performance → SecOps → Dependency → Infrastructure → DevOps → Rollback → Documentation → Reviewer] → PRs
```

## Key Files

- `src/main.rs` — CLI dispatch, subcommand handlers
- `src/pipeline/mod.rs` — `DEFAULT_AGENTS` ordering, `is_blocking()` classification
- `src/pipeline/agent.rs` — Ralph Loop: builds prompt, runs AI CLI, checks completion
- `src/provider/mod.rs` — Provider trait (CLI name, build args, session extraction)
- `src/config.rs` — All configuration from .env + CLI flags + env vars
- `agents/_base-system.md` — shared instructions inherited by ALL agents
